room_title: Escape room "Apartment 408" by Crimson Key in San Jose
room_description:
A recent series of murders have plagued the quiet town of Hill Valley. You've become very concerned about your best friend, Michael Morgan. His wife was one of the killerâ€™s victims, and you haven't heard from him in weeks. When he won't return any of your phone calls, you gather some mutual friends to go check on him.
When you arrive at his apartment, something has gone horribly wrong. Will the clues left behind lead you to safety, or will you end up another victim of the Hill Valley killer?
